<p><center><img src="http://i935.photobucket.com/albums/ad199/smcfarland2/04dea032-1dce-4f63-8873-84bb727e5780_zpsw8meag9q.jpg" border="0" alt=" photo 04dea032-1dce-4f63-8873-84bb727e5780_zpsw8meag9q.jpg"></center>
<br><center><b><font color="orange"><big>Come join an incredible team and work for a <b><br> Top Company to Work for in Arizona!</b></font></b> </center></big><br>
<hr>
<p><b><center><big><font color="blue">Vi at Silverstone is currently hiring a full time Kitchen Attendant. </b></center></big></font>
<center><p><b>SALARY INFO: Hourly pay depends on experience PLUS INCREDIBLE BENEFITS!!</b></center>
<p>
Vi's benefits are offered to foster personal growth, and keep you and your family healthy. Our <b><font color="blue">AMAZING</b></font> benefits include a choice between two comprehensive medical plans, prescription drug coverage, two dental plans, vision care for employees and dependents at no cost to the employee or an enhanced vision plan, flexible spending accounts for health and dependent care, <b>TUITION REIMBURSEMENT</b>, 401k with <b>GENEROUS</b> company match, pet insurance, legal coverage, <b>FREE</b> short and long term disability, <b>FREE</b> life insurance, employee assistance program, employee discount program and a <b>great PTO plan</b>. <br>
<br><b><font color="blue">Vi</font></b> also offers an incredible environment to work, learn and grow with development opportunities, leadership training and a free online learning system with access to over <i>1,000 courses</i>!<br>
<br>
An opportunity exists on our highly accomplished culinary team to provide support to the F&amp; B Department to include cleaning kitchen areas, perform storeroom maintenance and deliver food and beverage carts to appropriate areas.   The selected candidate may also set up public areas or help in dining area.   <br>
<br>

<u><b>Work Experience</b></u>: 
<br> Prior restaurant or customer service experience
<br> Experience that illustrates dependability 
<br> High school diploma or GED preferred 
<br>

<br><b><font color="blue"><center>If you are someone that is looking to join a strong, supportive and stable team that offers creative ideas<br> and wants to make a difference in providing the best care, you will be an excellent fit for our community. </b></font></center>
<br><center><p><a href="https://jobs.viliving.com/job/VILIA005J885/Kitchen-Attendant?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=craigslist&amp;utm_campaign=craigslist-feed" rel="nofollow"><b>Click Here To Apply</b></a></center><br>
<p> Vi is an equal opportunity employer. 
<p>
Keywords:  dishwasher, utility, kitchen, steward
</p></p></p></p></p></p></p>    </section>

